  "texts": [
    "Hadn't he seen the atrocities committed by the people of Nineveh?",
    "Hadn't he heard the cries of their victims?",
    "One day, as Jonah sat brooding, he noticed a group of women approaching him.",
    "They were dressed in tattered clothes and carried baskets filled with bread and water.",
    "Jonah recognized them as widows, women whose husbands had been killed in the violence that had once plagued Nineveh."
  ],
